---
title: Chicken Cutlets a l’Orange with Thyme-Scented Mashed Potatoes & Roasted Green Beans
description: Treat your taste buds to a trip—no passport required! This riff on a classic French dish—duck a l’orange—features quick-cooking chicken cutlets in a jammy orange sauce. The saucy, savory-sweet meat is paired with thyme-infused mashed potatoes and crisp roasted green beans for a restaurant-worthy meal that’s ready in just 35 minutes from start to finish.
